Name: Average resolution time after 'Accepted + Wait' until 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total time spent in 'Accepted + Wait' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time spent in 'Accepted + Wait' before moving to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Accepted + Assigned' across variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Total time from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Completed + Closed' for cases passing through 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average delay time in 'Accepted + Wait' due to 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment occurs

Name: Total resolution time of cases involving 'Accepted + Wait' and ending with 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum resolution time of cases starting with 'Accepted + Wait' and ending with 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average time it takes from 'Accepted + Wait' to the next activity in the most frequent variant
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Total time spent in 'Accepted + Wait' for cases that also involve 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + Wait - User occurs

Name: Average time between 'Accepted + Wait' and 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' across all relevant cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Minimum time from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Accepted + Assigned' in the shortest process variant
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Elapsed time between 'Accepted + Wait' and 'Completed + In Call' for cases following this path
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Time until 'Accepted + Wait' from case start for cases that begin with 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait'

Name: 'Accepted + Wait' cycle time as the duration from the start to the end of 'Accepted + Wait' within a case lifecycle
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Wait'
